Malaysia to Focus on Cutting Deficit in 2012 Budget, Najib Says

-- B y   S h a m i m   A d a m
-- 
2011-10-06T08:11:21Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-06/malaysia-to-focus-on-cutting-deficit-in-2012-budget-najib-says.html
Malaysia will announce new policies
to help citizens cope with living costs while remaining
“fiscally responsible” when Prime Minister Najib Razak
delivers the annual budget tomorrow, the premier’s office said
in a statement today.  “This budget will be about the government delivering on
our promise to ensure social justice while keeping our country
on the strong economic course that will deliver long-term
prosperity for all,” Najib said. “I am totally focused on
maintaining economic growth and cutting the deficit.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
Shamim Adam in  Kuala Lumpur  at 
